Class VersionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.VersionInfo

  • public final class VersionInfo
extends Object
    Information about a version of an Item that forms part of an ItemHistory.
    Since:
    2.0

    • Constructor Summary

      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getComment()
      Gets a String containing a comment made by the user to describe why a new version was made.
      ItemIdentifier getMergeSource()
      Gets the ItemIdentifier of the Item that acted as the source in the merge operation that created the version described by this VersionInfo.
      String getPrincipalName()
      Gets a String containing the name of the principal that created the Item version described by this VersionInfo.

      Gets a PropertyValue containing the creation date and time of the Item version described by this VersionInfo.

      Gets the VersionChangeType of the change that created the Item version described by this VersionInfo.

      Sets the comment associated with the creation of this version to the specified String.

      • setMergeSource

        public void setMergeSource(ItemIdentifier mergeSource)
        Sets the Item that acted as the source in the merge operation that created the version described by this VersionInfo to the one with the specified ItemIdentifier. When getMergeSource() returns a non-null value, getVersionChangeType() must return VersionChangeType.DATA.
        Parameters:
        mergeSource - The ItemIdentifier of the Item that acted as the source in the merge operation.
        Since:
        4.0

      • getMergeSource

        public ItemIdentifier getMergeSource()
        Gets the ItemIdentifier of the Item that acted as the source in the merge operation that created the version described by this VersionInfo.
        Returns:
        See above, or null if this VersionInfo is not associated with a merge operation.
        Since:
        4.0
